N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4231.16 - Money held pending determination

State Regulations

Pending the determination of an objection any prize which
the horse objected to may have won or may win in the race, or any money held by
the association holding the meeting, as the price of a horse claimed (if
affected by the determination of the objection), shall be withheld until the
objection is determined. Notes
